---
title: Cajun Shrimp Sandwich  with Spicy Remoulade and Charred Corn Slaw
description: These Cajun-style shrimp sandwiches deliver on spice and everything nice! With a do-it-yourself spicy remoulade sauce and refreshing sweet corn coleslaw, these filling sandwiches bring the excitement and the heat!
